## Analysis Workflow

- Multiplex spatial imaging was performed using the Akoya Phenocycler-Fusion platform.
- Senescence-associated markers including GLB1, p21, HMGB1, Lamin B1, AGER, SCEL, CD68, Pan-Cytokeratin, CD31, and Ki67 were evaluated.
- Cell-type composition and marker quantification analyses were performed using spatial imaging data.
- Statistical visualizations were generated using GraphPad Prism.

